Content: [telegram] <Regnar> The thing is most competitions have prizes. And those prizes are donated by community members, so they want to make sure there is a real value gained from the competition. As a potential donor I wouldn't want a competition until it's out of beta, any critical bugs are fixed, and a stress test is done. When we know we can handle a full scale trading competition on the DEX, itll be a good time for it. Until then, it is in beta. (re @Bar_Harbor: Should of been a trading competition)
